@startuml
title E Visa Processing And Follow Up System - State Diagram

[*] --> AccountCreated

state "Account Created" as AccountCreated
state "Logged In" as LoggedIn
state "Application Applied" as ApplicationApplied
state "View Status" as ViewStatus
state "Check Status" as CheckStatus
state "Cancelled Application" as CancelledApplication
state "Modified Details" as ModifiedDetails
state "Viewed Details" as ViewedDetails
state "Viewed Purpose" as ViewedPurpose
state "Feedback Given" as FeedbackGiven
state "Logged Out" as LoggedOut

AccountCreated --> LoggedIn : Create Account

LoggedIn --> ApplicationApplied : Apply For Visa
LoggedIn --> ViewStatus : View Status
ViewStatus --> CheckStatus : Check Status
CheckStatus --> ViewStatus : View Status
ApplicationApplied --> ViewStatus : View Status
LoggedIn --> CancelledApplication : Cancel Application
LoggedIn --> ModifiedDetails : Modify Details
ModifiedDetails --> ViewedDetails : View Details
ViewedDetails --> ViewedPurpose : View Purpose
ViewedPurpose --> ViewStatus : View Status
ViewedPurpose --> FeedbackGiven : Give Feedback
FeedbackGiven --> LoggedOut : Log Out
CancelledApplication --> LoggedOut : Log Out
ApplicationApplied --> ViewStatus : View Status

@enduml
